		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Personally I have no remorse for players who don't bother to sit through potentially vital information.  If you can't be bothered to watch for objectives then maybe you should be playing a different game.
<br />
<br />Cutscenes should be skippable but that doesn't mean they need to also be irrelevant to playing the game itself.  The player pays the price for not paying attention, whether it's a monster attacking him from behind or a scene telling him what he needs to know.

		

