<br />
<br />That's clearly different.  RTFM if you don't understand the core game mechanics.
<br />
<br />A clever game designer will put a "how to play" or "tutorial" option on the main menu to explain the rules of the game if they aren't immediately clear... rather than automatically show a cutscene the user is likely to skip.
<br />
<br />They can choose to see the tutorial or choose not to.  But they'll know it's there, and if they can't figure out the game mechanics on their own, they'll give it a look.

		

